37
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,600
This isn't the time for that.

38
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:16,480
Go to the nurse's office first.

39
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,360
Come on, hurry up.

40
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:22,720
Director,

41
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,000
please give this letter to Su Ruo.

42
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:25,800
Can you do that?

43
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,520
Hang in there.

44
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:32,200
Director,

45
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,320
You've confiscated a lot from us before,

46
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,960
