47
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,320
Please give it to her.

48
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:44,480
Alright, alright.

49
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:45,960
After the exam is over,

50
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,200
I'll make sure she gets it.

51
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,080
Good.

52
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,680
Su Ruo,

53
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,040
Stay alive.

