72
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,360
Don't be mad.

73
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,480
I'm not.

74
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,440
Su Ruo,

75
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:52,400
You look great in white.

76
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,120
Thanks.

77
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:56,560
I want a fresh start in college.

78
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,680
So I won't fall for someone

79
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,000
who likes someone else.

80
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,600
How's my perm? Does it look good?

81
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,280
It does.

82
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,560
Got a perm.

83
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:18,200
See?

84
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:19,840
Zhang Jie even got a perm.

85
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,280
Darn it.

86
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,680
Hui Ge,

87
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:23,920
what are you reading?

88
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,880
Tsinghua's extracurricular materials.

89
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:26,680
Don't mind me.

90
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:35,400
Tsinghua?

91
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:38,160
How do you know your score?

92
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:39,720
You can just estimate it.

93
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,480
It's easy.

94
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,000
Impressive, Hui Ge.

95
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:44,600
Ren Nan,

96
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,880
where are you going this summer?

97
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:47,960
Yunhai is pretty nice.

98
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:49,440
I just got back from there.

99
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,960
Seafood is super cheap.

100
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,760
You already went on a trip?

101
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,960
No, just went to see the sea.

102
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,880
Not really a vacation.

103
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,360
As for me,

104
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,680
I'm planning after the results

105
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,400
to travel abroad.

106
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:04,800
If you need help,

107
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,720
I know Yunhai's resorts well.

108
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,520
Just mention my name,

109
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:11,000
and you'll get a discount.

110
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:12,320
Alright.

111
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,360
Thanks.

112
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,360
That's odd.

113
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,520
I don't remember writing this.

114
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,400
You forgot?

115
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:33,640
You bought this book for me.

116
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:35,320
Then Teacher Jiang confiscated it.

117
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,240
Oh, right.

118
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,800
Can you get it back for me?

119
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:39,320
And return it to me, okay?

120
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:42,480
I don't remember that at all.

121
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:44,080
Just go get it back for me.

122
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:46,080
And make it my graduation gift.

123
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,320
Please?

124
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,000
Alright.

125
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:53,480
Su Ruo,

126
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,600
can I ask you something?

127
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:57,400
People say we're close,

128
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,240
but I always feel

129
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:01,400
we're not that close.

130
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:04,640
Are we friends?

131
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,760
Silly,

132
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,240
of course we're friends.

133
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,840
Is everyone doing okay?

134
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:25,640
Good.

135
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:27,840
Let yourselves go, right?

136
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:30,240
Anyway, the college entrance exam is over.

137
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,000
Go for it.

138
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,400
Teacher Jiang.

139
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:34,120
You're dressed in such a bold red.

140
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,560
It's graduation, after all.

141
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:37,920
Make a wonderful memory.

142
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,920
I promised you all before

143
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,400
that the things I confiscated

144
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,440
would be returned to you

145
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,600
when you graduate.

146
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:47,560
Take your own things.

147
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,680
Slam Dunk.

148
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,320
This is Zhang Xun's, right?

149
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,080
Take it.

150
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,680
Teacher Jiang, it's for you.

151
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,000
Take it.

152
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:11,280
The Laws of Time Travel.

153
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,720
Besides reading more books,

154
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,360
learn some social skills.

155
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:21,040
Teacher Jiang, I understand people,

156
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:21,960
but not the ways of the world.

157
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:33,240
You did your makeup well today.

158
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,080
How about

159
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:34,960
I don't give it back?

160
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:35,640
I want it.

161
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,640
Norwegian Wood.

162
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,560
Who is this drawing of?

163
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,440
Su Ruo.

164
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:52,640
Su Ruo.

165
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:53,800
Who drew it?

166
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:03,240
Yu Xingchen, I mean you.

167
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:04,760
You're an adult now.

168
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:07,640
Why don't you have that old drive anymore?

169
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,760
Teacher Jiang,

170
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:11,800
I didn't draw it.

171
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:12,960
I can't draw.

172
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,960
You think I'm senile?

173
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,080
Yu Xingchen, I personally

174
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,480
confiscated this from you.

175
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:18,760
Take it.

176
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,680
Go get it.

177
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,520
Hurry up.

178
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:22,720
Go on, go get it.

179
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:23,880
Go.

180
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,080
It's a pretty good drawing.

181
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:35,000
Maybe you should apply to art school.

182
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:47,120
I know this past year

183
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:49,040
felt very long for you all.

184
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:51,560
But time is relative.

185
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:53,560
What you think is past

186
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:56,320
may come back at some point.

187
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:59,240
What you think is far in the future

188
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:01,120
is actually right in front of you.

189
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:04,320
Maybe you don't quite understand

190
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,240
what I'm saying.

191
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,720
I'm saying the future isn't far.

192
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,680
Very soon,

193
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:11,760
you'll be my age.

194
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:13,800
So, as your teacher,

195
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,960
I hope on your journey ahead

196
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:17,920
you always remember

197
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:20,120
these three years of high school

198
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:22,800
and the friendship between classmates.

199
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,800
In life's big exam,

200
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:30,400
I hope you all get the results you deserve.

201
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:31,960
Class dismissed.

202
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:32,920
Stand up.

203
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,120
Classmates,

204
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,120
goodbye.

205
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,680
We graduated.

206
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:47,520
No matter which space-time we're in,

207
00:11:58,520 --> 00:11:59,280
Alright.

208
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,200
Comrades,

209
00:12:00,680 --> 00:12:01,480
See you out there.

210
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:02,800
Bye.

211
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:04,000
Bye.

212
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:53,680
